      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783182963207,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core Entities (Mostly from Functional Requirements)\n\n- User\n- Ride\n- Driver\n- Location",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Entities (Mostly from Functional Requirements)\n\n- User\n- Ride\n- Driver\n- Location",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "FPrIaS5NBlZbHLigUVArc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 232.9979409690156,
      "y": 372.8369412625335,
      "width": 1034,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2013430724,
      "version": 256,
      "versionNonce": 2102541007,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783182932192,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements (Features)\n\n- User can request to book a transportation service\n- User will be shown an estimated fare by inputting source and destination location\n- User should be able to request a ride with a Nearby Driver(s) by selecting an estimated fare\n- Drivers should be able to deny / accept a ride request.\n- Driver should be able to navigate to pickup and drop location.\n\nOut of Scope\n\n- User can select a mode / type of transportation\n- Rating of Drivers and Passengers / Users\n- Scheduling Rides",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements (Features)\n\n- User can request to book a transportation service\n- User will be shown an estimated fare by inputting source and destination location\n- User should be able to request a ride with a Nearby Driver(s) by selecting an estimated fare\n- Drivers should be able to deny / accept a ride request.\n- Driver should be able to navigate to pickup and drop location.\n\nOut of Scope\n\n- User can select a mode / type of transportation\n- Rating of Drivers and Passengers / Users\n- Scheduling Rides",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9yseSTfbP3JH3QWC429Yq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 249.37534092150992,
      "y": 948.2445436753405,
      "width": 592.8997192382812,
      "height": 529.4871794871796,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "az",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2081868100,
      "version": 1035,
      "versionNonce": 412835951,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "sjDs9tKAbRU4pcvKo_TW4",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1783231894305,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API (Entities Fulfilling Functional Requirements)\n\n- POST /ride/estimate_fare  -> Ride\n    {\n        pickup_location={lat, long},\n        drop_location={lat, long}\n    } \n- PATCH /ride/request?ride_id=1231234 -> Response Status\n- POST /location/driver -> Response Status\n    {\n        driver_location={lat, long}\n    }\n- PATCH /ride/response?ride_id=1231234 -> DriverRideDTO\n    {\n        ride_id,\n        action=ACCEPT/DENY\n    }\n- POST /ride/status\n    {\n        ride_id=1231234,\n        status=PICKED_UP / DROPPED_OFF\n    }",
      "fontSize": 19.254079254079258,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API (Entities Fulfilling Functional Requirements)\n\n- POST /ride/estimate_fare  -> Ride\n    {\n        pickup_location={lat, long},\n        drop_location={lat, long}\n    } \n- PATCH /ride/request?ride_id=1231234 -> Response Status\n- POST /location/driver -> Response Status\n    {\n        driver_location={lat, long}\n    }\n- PATCH /ride/response?ride_id=1231234 -> DriverRideDTO\n    {\n        ride_id,\n        action=ACCEPT/DENY\n    }\n- POST /ride/status\n    {\n        ride_id=1231234,\n        status=PICKED_UP / DROPPED_OFF\n    }",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
